.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-SET-PRIVATE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-set-private \- set a channel to private (unannounced)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-set-private
.I channel_id
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sets the specified channel to private/unannounced mode via CLN's setchannel command.
.PP
Output: JSON response from CLN's setchannel command.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-enable (1),
.BR lightning-channel-disable (1)
